furniture (3370) were inaccurately titled in the Standard Make and Use Tables (before 
redefinitions) at the detailed level in the 2002 Benchmark Input-Output Accounts.  The estimate
values are not impacted by the mis-titling.  The correct industry/commodity titles and related NAICS codes are:
